CREATE TRIGGER on_auth_user_created AFTER INSERT ON auth.users FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION handle_new_user()
CREATE TRIGGER posts_search_update BEFORE INSERT OR UPDATE ON public.posts FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION posts_search_update()
CREATE TRIGGER on_public_user_deleted AFTER DELETE ON public.users FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION handle_user_delete()
CREATE TRIGGER tr_check_filters BEFORE INSERT OR UPDATE ON realtime.subscription FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION realtime.subscription_check_filters()
CREATE TRIGGER update_objects_updated_at BEFORE UPDATE ON storage.objects FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION storage.update_updated_at_column()
CREATE TRIGGER secrets_encrypt_secret_trigger_secret BEFORE INSERT OR UPDATE OF secret ON vault.secrets FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION vault.secrets_encrypt_secret_secret()
